title: About Me
text:
I’m an MPhil student in applied psychology. I work in areas such as VR’s psychological impact, nature connectedness, and behavioural change.
This site documents my learning, progress, and reflections along the way.

title: Welcome
text:
Welcome to My Research Blog
This is a space where I reflect on research ideas, share updates on ongoing projects, and explore topics in applied and social psychology.
